abstract: ATLANTIC CITY, Oct. 7 (AP) --Flag Raiser won the $28,575 Atlantic City Handicap today,  giving his jockey, Howard Grant, his fourth victory of the day.
headline_main: 4-1 SHOT SCORES IN $28,575 EVENT; Spring Double Finishes 2d --Strate Stuff, $109, Victor at Hawthorne
